Package: ardoise-cobol-ide
Version: 1.0.0
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libgtk-4-1 (>= 4.0), libvte-2.91-gtk4-0, libncurses6, gnucobol
Recommends: gnucobol
Maintainer: Ento9 <ento9@example.com>
Description: Ardoise COBOL IDE — Hybrid GTK4 COBOL Editor
 A lightweight hybrid IDE for editing and running COBOL programs.
 Combines a GTK4 graphical interface with an embedded ncurses-based
 editor (CWSE) running inside a VTE terminal.
 .
 Features:
  - Sidebar file browser with folder navigation
  - Integrated VTE terminal with Catppuccin Mocha theme
  - One-click COBOL file creation and editing
  - Automatic CWSE engine embedding (no external binary needed)
  - Keyboard-first ncurses editor for maximum efficiency
 .
 Required dependencies (auto-installed):
  - GTK 4 runtime (libgtk-4-1)
  - VTE terminal widget for GTK4 (libvte-2.91-gtk4-0)
  - ncurses terminal library (libncurses6)
  - GnuCOBOL compiler (gnucobol)
